graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Backend[Backend API Server<br/>Fastify/Node.js<br/>8080/TCP]
        Frontend[Frontend Web UI<br/>React/PatternFly<br/>SPA]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift OAuth<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        StaticServer[Static File Server<br/>Fastify Static]

        OAuthProxy -->|forwards requests| Backend
        Backend -->|serves| Frontend
        Backend -->|serves| StaticServer
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token| OAuthProxy

    subgraph "Custom Resources (CRDs)"
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    Backend -->|creates/reads| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|reads| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|reads| OdhQuickStart
    Backend -->|CRUD| AcceleratorProfile

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus Service<br/>9091/TCP HTTP]
        ImageRegistry[Image Registry<br/>5000/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Backend -->|user impersonation| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|authentication| OAuthServer
    Backend -->|metrics queries| Prometheus
    Backend -->|ImageStream ops| ImageRegistry

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
        KubeflowNotebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRs]
        KServe[KServe<br/>ServingRuntime]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRs]
        OpenShiftBuild[OpenShift Build Service<br/>BuildConfigs]
    end

    Backend -->|watches| ODHOperator
    Backend -->|CRUD| KubeflowNotebooks
    Backend -->|reads| KServe
    Backend -->|CRUD| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|creates| OpenShiftBuild

    style Backend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Frontend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
